<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
        .wrapper { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d0d0d 0%, #000000 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #0f0f0f; border: 1px solid #1a1a1a; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .header { padding: 40px 0; background-color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 1px solid #222; }
        .logo { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 900; color: #e50914; letter-spacing: -2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: italic; }
        .content { padding: 40px; text-align: left; }
        .greeting { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .description { font-size: 16px; color: #aaaaaa; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        
        .notice-card { background: #141414; border: 1px solid #333; border-left: 4px solid #e50914; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 30px 0; }
        .notice-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #e50914; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .notice-text { font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.5; }
        
        .btn-wrapper { margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #333; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 35px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; border: 1px solid #444; }
        
        .footer { padding: 40px; text-align: center; color: #444444; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo">CineTube</div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="greeting" style="color: #ffffff;">We're sorry to see you go.</div>
                <p class="description" style="color: #aaaaaa;">This email confirms that your subscription has been cancelled. We've enjoyed having you as part of our audience.</p>
                
                <div class="notice-card">
                    <div class="notice-title" style="color: #e50914;">Access Expiry</div>
                    <div class="notice-text" style="color: #ffffff;">Your premium access will remain active until <strong><%= expiryDate %></strong>. After this date, your account will revert to a Free plan.</div>
                </div>

                <p class="description" style="color: #aaaaaa;">Changed your mind? You can reactivate your subscription at any time to resume uninterrupted streaming.</p>

                <div class="btn-wrapper">
                    <a href="<%= envVars.FRONTEND_URL %>" class="btn">Return to CineTube</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> CineTube Cinema. All rights reserved.<br>
                You are receiving this because a cancellation was processed for your CineTube account.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
